            "title": "Putin Critic Alexei Navalny 'Could Die At Any Moment,' Doctor Says - NPR",
            "description": "The imprisoned Russian opposition leader, who is three weeks into a hunger strike, is at risk of cardiac arrest or kidney failure according to test results, his physician says.",
