                "author": "Harry Howard, Martin Robinson, Rory Tingle",
                "title": "Prince Charles says his 'dear papa' Prince Philip would be 'deeply touched' by sorrow at his death",
                "description": "In a pre-recorded video message, the Prince of Wales said his father had given 'the most remarkable, devoted service' to 'The Queen, to my family and to the country'.",
