                "description": "(Bloomberg) -- Bitcoin plunged the most in more than seven weeks, just days after reaching a record.The token fell 8.5% to $55,689.98 as of 1:48 p.m. in...",
                "url": "https://finance.yahoo.com/news/bitcoin-plunges-biggest-intraday-drop-055211037.html",
